Name: Vector Born
About the game: Vector Born is an arcade bullet-hell style game. Travel planet to planet through an unknown solar system to find out why you have woken up with no memory. Each planet is packed full of alien ships bent on destroying you. Collect weapon upgrades and shields to tear through these attackers. Unlock new ships to pilot. Take on the planets commanders. Unearth your forgotten past. Vector Born is a fully playable game at the moment but there is much more to come. Future updates may include an even more diverse array of weapons and playable characters, special attacks and abilities, a leveling system, store aspect, many more levels, enemies, and bosses.
